{
  "stem": "6258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father, who didn't wanted-- well, to be connected with this so-called, Jewish-- how to say, Jewish elders, [GERMAN]-- well, you know-- I don't know what is that English word for it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, there was-- there was the head of the community.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- and there was already Jewish police, Ordenienst, called OD.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, but they were the people who were preparing least for deportation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all these things, my father didn't wanted this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, therefore, he choose to be head of this sanitation department.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at least, he thought he will be able to be useful socially by cleaning-- his people were cleaning the ghetto, and the streets, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Mother was working with the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I attended still the clandestine classes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And also, since there was no school, I took care of some two or three small children whose parents were working outside of the ghetto, so that the kids will have someone.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was making drawings for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I rewrote my own children's book.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I was like a nanny for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But not too long, because then when there was the first big action-- action it was called-- then all the children left.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was something else also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That this-- they-- the words the Germans used, like Aussiedlung, translocation, or so, they sound quite innocent.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody knew that this is translocation out of this world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then, suddenly, people who were in the suburbs of Krakow were coming to the Krakow Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the Germans directed them to come to the Krakow ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
